    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for me\u2014perfect for someone who wants a reliable car that still looks and feels great on the road! I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with the basics, so it's ready to hit the pavement as soon as you grab the keys. If you're looking for a well-loved car that's got plenty of life left in it, come take a look! Happy to chat if you have any questions!",
      "price": 31500.0,
