    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between daily utility and premium comfort. The exterior presents beautifully, maintaining a deep gloss with only minor, negligible imperfections consistent with careful ownership. Inside, you\u2019ll find a pristine, smoke-free cabin featuring supple upholstery and fully operational electronics. Mechanically, this car is turn-key; it has been strictly serviced according to the manufacturer's schedule, resulting in a smooth, responsive drive and a whisper-quiet engine. Recently fitted with new tires and having just undergone a comprehensive fluid service, it is ready for the open road. This is a dependable, high-quality choice for a discerning buyer who values both performance and aesthetic appeal.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
